The paper proposes a framework for reasoning over knowledge graphs using embeddings in vector space, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with handling logical queries, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper involves working with large-scale and incomplete data, which is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB).
